*ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.21 (25 Dec 2003)

  25 Dec 2003; <rac@gentoo.org> ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.15-r1.ebuild,
  ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.15.ebuild, ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.16-r1.ebuild,
  ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.16.ebuild, ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.21.ebuild:
  Add ~arch .21 including self-tests. Clean house on .15 and .16s

  25 Dec 2003; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.20.ebuild:
  Marked stable on sparc.

  26 Dec 2003; <plasmaroo@gentoo.org> ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.15-r1.ebuild,
  ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.15.ebuild:
  Made stable on "x86" as SpamAssassin dependencies were broken by older
  versions getting removed.

  25 Dec 2003; Michael Cummings,,, <mcummings@gentoo.org>
  ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.11-r1.ebuild, ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.11.ebuild,
  ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.13.ebuild:
  No longer available on CPAN

