*ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.16 (24 Sep 2003)

  24 Sep 2003; <rac@gentoo.org> ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.11.ebuild,
  ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.13.ebuild, ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.15.ebuild,
  ExtUtils-MakeMaker-6.16.ebuild:
  Change how DESTDIR and PERLPREFIX are handled, to adapt to new MakeMaker
  semantics. Great thanks to Wayne Davison <gentoo@blorf.net> in bug 29447.

